    "body": "Actually there is already the `--enable-slashing-protection-history-pruning` flag that prune attesting records older than the current weak subjectivity period. However, this pruning process only runs at startup, so running the validator clients for weeks/months without reboot will still fill the Bolt DB.\r\n\r\n==> Implementing the minimal slashing DB is still useful.",
